<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="reason-v">reason <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'riːzn/    美 /'riːzn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>推理；劝说；辩论：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>Reasoning with</strong> them is a waste of time. 
和他们讲道理是浪费时间。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>推断；推论：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We <strong>reasoned</strong> (<strong>that</strong>) if we started early in the morning, we would get there by noon.
我们推断如果一大早出发的话，中午之前就能到达那里。</p></div></div>